    "body": "@murgatroid99 thanks for answer.\r\n\r\nI've checked this and see that if I run two instances of the gRPC server, than for both the `Server.bind('0.0.0.0:50051', ...)` returns the value `50051`. It does not return `0` for the instance which was started second (as I naively expect). Is it correct behavior?"
