    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Unless there's a major bug somewhere, that output is correct, and both servers are bound to that port. gRPC automatically binds ports with SO_REUSEPORT, so multiple gRPC servers can actually successfully bind the same port at the same time."
  },
